0.1.name: wordpress/enhancing-js
0.1.description:
Enhancing JS plugin will enable to edit external JavaScript. This JavaScript is output through WordPress rewrite API. In addition, this plugin implements simple visual editor for JavaScript.

If you will install this plugin with 'Enhancing CSS' plugin, You can customize themes without PHP programming!

  • Plugin Homepage
  • Support

Some features:

  • You can edit External JavaScript on visual editor.
  • You can manage WordPress Default JavaScript frameworks.
  • Conditional GET and ETag support.

Translators:

  • Japanese(ja) - Takayuki Miyauchi

You can send your own language pack to me.
